CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "Dazzling D.I.s were presented to the guests Sunday night at their MENDS benefit show and dance at Holiday House. Left to right: Evelyn Christian, Juanita Drake, Birdie Dunlap, Gloria Grate, Mary Jean Eaton and Margaret Watson. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six D. I. Club members wearing identical light colored outfits from left to right: Evelyn Christian, Juanita Drake, Birdie Dunlap, Gloria Golden Grate, Mary Jean Eaton, and Margaret Watson, standing in Holiday House for annual MENDS benefit
